{"id": "art-4712", "label": "Art. 4712", "title": "Art. 4712: Programe de formare şi perfecţionare", "slug": "art-4712", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_283486321\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1641\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_283486321\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><u><span style='color:#569748'>Art. 47<sup>12</sup>:\nPrograme de formare &#351;i perfec&#355;ionare </span></u></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1766430754\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1640\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1766430754\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(1)Persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup> alin.\n(1) beneficiaz&#259;, la momentul numirii în func&#355;ie &#351;i pe perioada\nmandatului sau exercit&#259;rii func&#355;iei, dup&#259; caz, de programe de\nformare specializat&#259; &#351;i perfec&#355;ionare profesional&#259;\norganizate de Institutul Na&#355;ional de Administra&#355;ie, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii, pe teme referitoare la etica &#351;i conduita în\nexercitarea atribu&#355;iilor.</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_686948391\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1639\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_686948391\"><![endif]></span><u><span\nstyle='color:#569748'>(2)Cheltuielile aferente programelor de formare\nspecializat&#259; &#351;i perfec&#355;ionare profesional&#259; prev&#259;zute\nla alin. (1) sunt suportate din bugetul autorit&#259;&#355;ilor &#351;i\ninstitu&#355;iilor publice în care persoanele prev&#259;zute la art. 47<sup>2</sup>\nalin. (1) î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea.</span></u></p>"}